latestPosts.caption:
Thrilled to share this glam look for season 3 of Fabulous Lives vs Bollywood Wives ! ✨
Bringing to life the Japanese elegance juxtaposed with a beautiful kimono splashed with vintage floral motifs, I have created this makeup look for a socialite ,fashion icon and the celebrity @kalyanisaha which is all about fresh dewy skin, winged eyes with a touch of moondust shimmer and a touch of brown on the crease line & the lower lid. 
The look has been kept casual with a touch of minimalist aesthetics. The nude lips enhances her sharp facial features which have been further highlighted with a Charlotte Tilbury blush in medium shade of Pillow Talk !
.
.
Her daughter  @tahira_tara ,the look i have  kept minimal which gives a very soft glam .
.
.
Watch now on Netflix "Fabulous Lives vs Bollywood Wives💫
#netflixseries #bollywoodwives #fabulouswivesvsbollywoodwives #glamourous

latestPosts.caption:
One couldn’t be prouder of his bestie @joshhynn for turning his passion into a profession—especially in his own hometown, giving back to the roots that shaped him.
At @accentuate.academy he’s committed to creating opportunities for young people to express their creativity, build confidence, and explore exciting career paths in makeup, hairstyling, and self-grooming.
